data.description: Discover this meticulously maintained 2,508 sq ft residence nestled in the charming Village of Armada! This captivating home features 5 bedrooms and 2 full baths, situated on a fenced corner lot with picturesque brick paver walkways. The expansive island kitchen boasts ample cupboard space, brand new LVT flooring, and comes complete with all appliances. Revel in the elegant touch of coved ceilings and choose between the spacious living room or the warm and cozy family room with a wood stove fireplace. Take note of the generously sized bedrooms, and appreciate the refreshed bathrooms with tub reglazing. The home offers separate heating for each level, with an attic fan equipped with its own remote. The crawl space is professionally foam insulated, and a convenient storage shed adds practicality to the property. Recent updates abound, with a 3D Shingle Roof installed (2018), Windows (2021), HWH (2021), Disposal (2022), Boiler (2014), Deck (2020). The Sewer Line was also partially replaced this year (2023). Enjoy the spacious front porch and extensive decking. Walking distance to downtown shopping, library, schools, park and bike trail (Macomb Orchard Trail). Bonus: qualifies for 0 down USDA Rural Dev financing. Act quickly to seize this fantastic opportunity!
